OL,3,CMan admits murdering mother-of-three
OL,4,Cin Portsmouth during trial
OL,6,FA man has admitted murdering a mother-
OL,7,Fof-three in Portsmouth last year on
OL,8,Fthe fifth day of his trial.
OL,10,FCharlie James Jeans, 31, of Margate
OL,11,FRoad in Southsea appeared at
OL,12,FPortsmouth Crown Court this afternoon
OL,13,F(Monday 15 June) and changed his plea,
OL,14,Fadmitting to the murder of Samantha
OL,15,FMurphy.
OL,17,FOfficers were called at 7:37am on
OL,18,FThursday 5 June 2025 to a report that
OL,19,Fthe body of 32-year-old Samantha had
OL,20,Fbeen found at a house on Wadham Road
OL,21,Fin Portsmouth.
